channel.description:
Hello, and first off, this is the RS2 Server [size=20pt]DEVELOPMENT[/size]/help. keyword: Development
This server is currently in development and im trying to make it one of the best [u]silab[/u] servers ever. Yes you heard me, [b]SILAB[/b]. Most people hate silab, and so do I, but im gonna try to bring it to the max and make a server that everyone will enjoy named
[b][size=30pt]PROJECT ICE[/size][/b]
Table of contents:
1. PICS! 2. Goals 3. Q & A
adding more soon.
Here are some pics so far.
[IMG]http://i427.photobucket.com/albums/pp352/Ice_riddles/custombank.jpg[/img]
[URL=http://img183.imageshack.us/my.php?image=projecticesc9.png][IMG]http://img183.imageshack.us/img183/8950/projecticesc9.th.png[/img][/URL]
[URL=http://img504.imageshack.us/my.php?image=projectice2yf6.png][IMG]http://img504.imageshack.us/img504/4279/projectice2yf6.th.png[/img][/URL]
[URL=http://img147.imageshack.us/my.php?image=projectice3xh5.png][IMG]http://img147.imageshack.us/img147/4489/projectice3xh5.th.png[/img][/URL]
[URL=http://img379.imageshack.us/my.php?image=projectice4cv0.png][IMG]http://img379.imageshack.us/img379/9527/projectice4cv0.th.png[/img][/URL]
Ok, thats it for pictures.
!GOALS!
right now im trying to make it hard to get money, 60% done.
!END OF GOALS!
Q & A ========================
Q: Watz y0u ip 1 w@nt t0 pl@y. A: It's not released yet.
Q:Aha your never gonna complete this you nub A:How can you be sure?
Q:Silab Sucks. A:Yes it does.
Q:When are you gonna be done? A:Idk yet.
[font=Green][b][size=30pt]UPDATES! - YES IM TYPING THEM NOW, PLEASE NOTE THIS IS NOT THE FIRST UPDATE I MADE IN THE SERVER, JUST THE FIRST ONE IM TYPING DOWN![/size][/b][/font]
[b][size=15pt][/size]UPDATE 1 -[/b]
Changed Harmony's hunting bow to dark bow :|
More to come! updated daily! More to come! Updated daily!
